{"tid":2117272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 香港服務性行業","createTime":"2020-07-20T17:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T19:38:42.000Z","uid":233104,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3623cc524ad204591e5b0e0e5d3d90a47cbf5ab9","tid":2117272,"uid":233104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:04:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">Sorry呃左大家入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然多年來大家都知，但今日翻完工都想講一句<br />\n<br />\n係香港做服務業真係賤過地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情咁嚴重啲高層為咗形象都可以唔理我哋安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲客不滿就大吵大鬧，又要投訴，為難人哋<br />\n<br />\n難聽嘅說話要幾多有幾多，甚至蠻不講理<br />\n<br />\n好多次唔係我哋態度唔好，都要比你鬧兩句，仲要多謝你<br />\n<br />\n最後希望睇到呢個post嘅大家可以以禮相待，尊重翻人哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">最後，大家盡量少啲出街，減輕醫護負擔</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f8bcbb06fc761783d2d6daadcde27ea462205a4","tid":2117272,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04715ccffae0ff3bee463a0b6abfcb469c21b053","tid":2117272,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1522a912490ae876fe0c8e98fc9c464bf3815cc","tid":2117272,"uid":233104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04715ccffae0ff3bee463a0b6abfcb469c21b053","tid":2117272,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f8bcbb06fc761783d2d6daadcde27ea462205a4","tid":2117272,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"係啊，唔介意生意差但唔需要咁掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5a91e994b225d4f6ebc